__pycache__/, *.pyc          ← Python cache
.env.yaml, sa-key.json       ← secrets
run_local.py                 ← local only
.claude/, claude-ML/         ← your Claude workspace
main.zip                     ← old archive
summary.md                   ← internal notes
gdrive-platform-document*    ← internal doc
Google Drive Intelligence*/  ← platform doc folder
drive_snapshot_*.csv         ← local snapshots
README.md, LICENSE           ← not needed on GCP